    "description": "Dalmia Bharat Holdings Services is actively seeking a talented and motivated Plant Manager to join our dynamic team in Navi Mumbai. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout Dalmia Bharat Holdings Services:\nDalmia Bharat Holdings Services is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with design and engineering teams on product improvements\n• Oversee daily production operations to meet output targets\n• Ensure product quality meets internal and customer specifications\n• Ensure environmental compliance and waste management\n• Maintain accurate production records and prepare daily reports\n• Implement lean manufacturing and continuous improvement initiatives\n• Manage supplier quality audits and vendor development\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in 5S\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in AutoCAD\n• Proficiency in PLC/SCADA\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n• Proficiency in APQP\n• Proficiency in Six Sigma\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Learning & development budget\n• Flexible working hours\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Navi Mumbai, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Dalmia Bharat Holdings Services!",
